### Product Tour API Requests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:5145
@token = your_jwt_token_here

### Login to get token (use Auth module)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/identity/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "test@example.com",
    "password": "TestPass123!"
}

### Set tour status to Todo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/me/tours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourKey": "onboarding-tour",
    "status": 0
}

### Set tour status to Done
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/me/tours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourKey": "dashboard-tour",
    "status": 1
}

### Set tour status to Closed
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/me/tours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourKey": "features-tour",
    "status": 2
}

### Update existing tour status (Done)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/me/tours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "tourKey": "onboarding-tour",
    "status": 1
}

### Get all tour statuses for current user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/profiles/me/tours
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Examples of tour keys
# "onboarding-tour" - Initial onboarding walkthrough
# "dashboard-tour" - Dashboard features tour
# "retro-creation-tour" - Retrospective creation guide
# "team-management-tour" - Team management features

### Status values:
# 0 = Done - User completed the tour
# 1 = Closed - User dismissed the tour without completing

